title: Gophers recruit Tyler Johnson stars as North moves to section finals
text: Tyler Johnson's 6 TDs lead Minneapolis North in rout of Belgrade-Brooten-Elrosa 10/20/2015, 5:45pm CDT By Tyler Mason, Special to the Star Tribune The quarterback, who has committed to play at Minnesota, ran for three scores and passed for three more in a 48-10 victory.
